The Label is too big or on an other position, then on .net Framework.
It overlaps partly the TextBox in the following program.

Here a screenshot:

![WinForms](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8337032/72198787-cb2db180-3432-11ea-9565-5670d86abced.png)

